rdf:Description.dc:title: RDA Item properties
rdf:Description.skos:note: Properties derived from RDA elements and relationship designators with the domain of RDA Item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: accompaniedByItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is accompanied by (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item brought together with another item after being issued.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item brought together with another item after being issued.

rdf:Description.reg:name: accompanyingItemRelationship
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has accompanying item relationship with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that accompanies or is accompanied by the item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that accompanies or is accompanied by the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: analysedInItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is analysed in (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a work that examines the source item to identify its components and their relations.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A work that examines the source item to identify its components and their relations.

rdf:Description.reg:name: annotator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has annotator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person who makes manuscript annotations on an item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A person who makes manuscript annotations on an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: autographer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has autographer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person whose manuscript signature appears on an item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A person whose manuscript signature appears on an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: binder
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has binder
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person who binds an item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A person who binds an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: boundWith
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is bound with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that has been bound within the same binding as the item being described.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that has been bound within the same binding as the item being described.

rdf:Description.reg:name: collectionRegistrar
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has collection registrar
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a curator who lists or inventories the items in an aggregate work such as a collection of items or works.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A curator who lists or inventories the items in an aggregate work such as a collection of items or works.

rdf:Description.reg:name: collector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has collector
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a curator who brings together items from various sources that are then arranged, described, and cataloged as a collection.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A curator who brings together items from various sources that are then arranged, described, and cataloged as a collection.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentaryInItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commentary in (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a work that contains a set of explanatory or critical notes on the described item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A work that contains a set of explanatory or critical notes on the described item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: containedInItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is contained in (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a larger item of which the item is a discrete component.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A larger item of which the item is a discrete component.

rdf:Description.reg:name: containerOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is container of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is a discrete component of a larger item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that is a discrete component of a larger item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: critiquedInItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is critiqued in (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a work that contains a critical evaluation of the described item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A work that contains a critical evaluation of the described item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: curator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has curator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body conceiving, aggregating, and/or organizing an exhibition, collection, or other item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A person, family, or corporate body conceiving, aggregating, and/or organizing an exhibition, collection, or other item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: currentOwner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has current owner
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body currently having legal possession of an item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A person, family, or corporate body currently having legal possession of an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: custodialHistoryOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has custodial history of item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a record of previous ownership or custodianship of an item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A record of previous ownership or custodianship of an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: custodian
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has custodian
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body having legal custody of an item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A person, family, or corporate body having legal custody of an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dedicateeOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dedicatee (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body to whom an item is dedicated.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A person, family, or corporate body to whom an item is dedicated.

rdf:Description.reg:name: depositor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has depositor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a current owner of an item who deposited the item into the custody of another person, family, or corporate body, while still retaining ownership.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A current owner of an item who deposited the item into the custody of another person, family, or corporate body, while still retaining ownership.

rdf:Description.reg:name: describedInItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is described in (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a work that describes a described item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A work that describes a described item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digitalTransferItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digital transfer (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item in a digital format that results from the transfer of an item in another digital format.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item in a digital format that results from the transfer of an item in another digital format.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digitalTransferOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digital transfer of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item in a digital format that is transferred to another digital format.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item in a digital format that is transferred to another digital format.

rdf:Description.reg:name: donor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has donor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a former owner of an item who donated that item to another owner.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A former owner of an item who donated that item to another owner.

rdf:Description.reg:name: electronicReproductionItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is electronic reproduction (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item in a digital format that is the result of the transfer of an item in analog format.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item in a digital format that is the result of the transfer of an item in analog format.

rdf:Description.reg:name: electronicReproductionOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is electronic reproduction of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item in an analog format that is transferred to a digital format.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item in an analog format that is transferred to a digital format.

rdf:Description.reg:name: equivalentItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is equivalent (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that exemplifies a manifestation that embodies the same expression of a work.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that exemplifies a manifestation that embodies the same expression of a work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: equivalentItemRelationship
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has equivalent item relationship with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is equivalent to the item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that is equivalent to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: evaluatedInItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is evaluated in (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a work that examines or judges the described item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A work that examines or judges the described item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: facsimileItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is facsimile (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that exactly reproduces an item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that exactly reproduces an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: facsimileOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is facsimile of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is used as the basis for an exact reproduction.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that is used as the basis for an exact reproduction.

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmedWithItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is filmed with (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is contained on the same microform with the item being described.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that is contained on the same microform with the item being described.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formerOwner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has former owner
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body formerly having legal possession of an item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A person, family, or corporate body formerly having legal possession of an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: honoureeOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has honouree (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body honoured by an item, e.g., a person to whom a copy is presented.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A person, family, or corporate body honoured by an item, e.g., a person to whom a copy is presented.

rdf:Description.reg:name: identifierForTheItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has identifier for the item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a character string associated with an item that serves to differentiate that item from other items.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A character string associated with an item that serves to differentiate that item from other items.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illuminator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has illuminator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person providing decoration to a specific item using precious metals or color, often with elaborate designs and motifs.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A person providing decoration to a specific item using precious metals or color, often with elaborate designs and motifs.

rdf:Description.reg:name: immediateSourceOfAcquisitionOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has immediate source of acquisition of item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to the source from which the agency directly acquired an item and the circumstances under which it was received.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitLabel: immediate source of acquisition of item
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: The source from which the agency directly acquired an item and the circumstances under which it was received.

rdf:Description.reg:name: inscriber
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has inscriber
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person who has written a statement of dedication or gift on an item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A person who has written a statement of dedication or gift on an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: manifestationExemplified
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has manifestation exemplified
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to the manifestation exemplified by an item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: The manifestation exemplified by an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnDimensionsOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on dimensions of item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a note providing information on the dimensions of the specific item being described that is not recorded as part of the dimensions element.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A note providing information on the dimensions of the specific item being described that is not recorded as part of the dimensions element.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnExtentOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on extent of item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a note providing information on the extent of the specific item being described that is not recorded as part of the extent element.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A note providing information on the extent of the specific item being described that is not recorded as part of the extent element.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a note providing information on attributes of the item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A note providing information on attributes of the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnItemSpecificCarrierCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on item-specific carrier characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a note providing additional information about carrier characteristics that are specific to the item being described and are assumed not to apply to other items exemplifying the same manifestation.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A note providing additional information about carrier characteristics that are specific to the item being described and are assumed not to apply to other items exemplifying the same manifestation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: onDiscWithItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is on disc with (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is contained on the same disc with the item being described.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that is contained on the same disc with the item being described.

rdf:Description.reg:name: otherPFCItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has other person, family, or corporate body associated with an item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body other than an owner or custodian associated with an item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitLabel: other person, family, or corporate body associated with an item
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A person, family, or corporate body other than an owner or custodian associated with an item. Includes curators, binders, restorationists, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: owner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has owner
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body having legal possession of an item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A person, family, or corporate body having legal possession of an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: preservationFacsimileItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is preservation facsimile (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that consists of an exact reproduction on preservation-quality media, such as acid-free permanent or archival paper.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that consists of an exact reproduction on preservation-quality media, such as acid-free permanent or archival paper.

rdf:Description.reg:name: preservationFacsimileOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is preservation facsimile of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is used as the basis for an exact reproduction on preservation-quality media, such as acid-free permanent or archival paper.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that is used as the basis for an exact reproduction on preservation-quality media, such as acid-free permanent or archival paper.

rdf:Description.reg:name: relatedItemOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related item of item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item, represented by an identifier or a description, that is related to the item being described (e.g., an item used as the basis for a microform reproduction).
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item, represented by an identifier or a description, that is related to the item being described (e.g., an item used as the basis for a microform reproduction).

rdf:Description.reg:name: reprintedAsItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is reprinted as (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is a reissue of an item that exemplifies another printed manifestation.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that is a reissue of an item that exemplifies another printed manifestation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: reprintOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is reprint of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that exemplifies a printed manifestation that is used as the basis for a reissue of a manifestation.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that exemplifies a printed manifestation that is used as the basis for a reissue of a manifestation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: reproducedAsItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is reproduced as (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that reproduces another item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that reproduces another item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: reproductionOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is reproduction of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is used as the basis for a reproduction.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that is used as the basis for a reproduction.

rdf:Description.reg:name: restorationist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has restorationist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for the set of technical, editorial, and intellectual procedures aimed at compensating for the degradation of an item by bringing it back to a state as close as possible to its original condition.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A person, family, or corporate body responsible for the set of technical, editorial, and intellectual procedures aimed at compensating for the degradation of an item by bringing it back to a state as close as possible to its original condition.

rdf:Description.reg:name: restrictionsOnAccessToItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has restrictions on access to item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to limitations placed on access to an item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: Limitations placed on access to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: restrictionsOnUseOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has restrictions on use of item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to limitations placed on uses such as reproduction, publication, exhibition, etc.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: Limitations placed on uses such as reproduction, publication, exhibition, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: reviewedInItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is reviewed in (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a work that contains a brief evaluation of the described item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A work that contains a brief evaluation of the described item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: seller
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has seller
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a former owner of an item who sold that item to another owner.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A former owner of an item who sold that item to another owner.

rdf:Description.reg:name: subjectOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is subject of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a work that is about the item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: A work that is about the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: wholePartItemRelationship
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has whole-part item relationship with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is contained in or contains the item.
rdf:Description.rdakit:toolkitDefinition: An item that is contained in or contains the item.
